text: Zach Latimer (born October 21, 1983 in Denver, Colorado) is a former American football linebacker. He played college football at the University of Oklahoma. His father, Don Latimer, played collegiate football for the University of Miami, and in the NFL for the Denver Broncos. ==External links== *Zach Latimer at SoonerSports.com Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Denver Category:American football linebackers Category:Oklahoma Sooners football players
